The paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques in wireless communication systems, which falls under the category of networked and distributed systems (cs.NI). The paper also focuses on scalability, which is a key concern in machine learning (cs.LG) and data science (cs.DS). The use of learning algorithms and model training strategies also falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper discusses the architecture and computing framework of scalable data-driven systems, which falls under the category of control and systems engineering (cs.SY).
